modName: Female High Elf Preset for ECE - Arisha
descriptionHtml:
This is my high elf character preset that I've tweaked and sculpted by hand over the past few years. I think this is as good as I can make her, so I've decided to share her appearance with anyone else who might be interested in using her looks.
